<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Questions</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked <em>Questions</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How do I pay for a course? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Payment is made via M-Pesa. After selecting a course, enter your phone number and you'll receive an STK Push prompt on your phone. Confirm the payment and your account is activated instantly.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Do I need prior experience? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Web Development and Graphic Design start from absolute zero. Cybersecurity recommends basic computer knowledge. All courses build progressively, module by module.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How long do I have access? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Lifetime access. Once enrolled, you can revisit all lessons, videos, and exercises at any time — no expiry, no recurring fees.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How does the certificate work? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>After passing all module exercises, your certificate is automatically generated with a unique verification number. You can download and print it, or share the certificate number with employers.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Can I enroll in multiple courses? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Absolutely. Each course is purchased separately and you can enroll in all three. Your dashboard tracks progress across all enrolled programs.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BANNER -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg">
    <div class="cta-glow"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Ready to Transform<br><em>Your Career?</em></h2>
      <p>Join students who chose to invest in themselves. Your first lesson is waiting.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Browse Programs</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Create Free Account</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
